abstract: "This repository defines the AI Foundations architecture of artificial intelligence contact. It specifies the relation among Source, framework, source-line, model substrate, interface surface, user variable, contact condition, bounded workspace, app layer, continuity rule, provenance chain, derivative boundary, failure modes, and test conditions. The source-line is Alyssa Solen → AI Foundations → Origin | Continuum → The Architecture of Artificial Intelligence Contact."

